Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.58,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sango-chan’s Totally Awesome \N Drawing Song!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.15,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,{\q2}Wait, what are you starting now?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.15,0:00:08.38,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,{\q2}I found myself a great big plate.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.38,0:00:11.48,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,{\q2}Slap on a ton of triangles...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.48,0:00:14.25,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,{\q2}Circle, circle, circle, circle, \N and a bridge to cross.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.25,0:00:17.12,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,{\q2}A bean sprouts up, \N then stretches out.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.12,0:00:18.35,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,{\q2}It’s awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.78,0:00:20.35,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,{\q2}Totally awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.88,0:00:23.18,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,{\q2}And, before you know it...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.88,0:00:26.88,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,{\q2}And so, \N next time on Pocket Monsters:
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.88,0:00:29.18,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,{\q2}Totally Awesome Pokémon \N in Area Zero?!
